# 🌐 HTTP Status Checker (Go + HTML)

A simple web app built with Go that checks the HTTP status of any URL and keeps a history log of your recent checks — all displayed on a clean Bootstrap UI.

---

## ✨ Features

- ✅ Enter any URL to check its HTTP status (e.g. `200 OK`, `404 Not Found`)
- 🕒 Maintains the 10 most recent checks in memory
- 💻 Clean and responsive UI with Bootstrap
- ⚡ Fast and lightweight (no database or frontend framework)

